Imiskoumbria, also known as Imiz is a hip-hop group from Athens, Greece. The group's roster has been the same since its inception in 1994, constisting of rapper Dimitris Mentzelos, Mithridatis (born Mithridatis Hatzihatzoglou) and DJ Pritanis (born Kostas Kostakos.
